1255  // value used in measurement timing budget calculations
1256  // assumes PresetMode is LOWPOWER_AUTONOMOUS
1257  //
1258  // vhv = LOWPOWER_AUTO_VHV_LOOP_DURATION_US + LOWPOWERAUTO_VHV_LOOP_BOUND
1259  // (tuning parm default) * LOWPOWER_AUTO_VHV_LOOP_DURATION_US
1260  // = 245 + 3 * 245 = 980
1261  // TimingGuard = LOWPOWER_AUTO_OVERHEAD_BEFORE_A_RANGING +
1262  // LOWPOWER_AUTO_OVERHEAD_BETWEEN_A_B_RANGING + vhv
1263  // = 1448 + 2100 + 980 = 4528
1264  static const uint32_t TimingGuard = 4528;
